description: "A map of the landing of British troops at Chillinching (Cilincing, 12 miles to the east of Batavia), part of the 1811 invasion of Java during the Napoleonic Wars. The frigate Leda is at the river mouth, as the British soldiers row to shore."
title: "The landing of the British Army at Chillinching on the island of Java 4th Augt. 1811"
